# Markdown Docs

- When implementing new middleware, tools, etc, create documentation under `[app-name]/docs` file. For example, for the server code, add docs on `server/docs/`. For client, add under the `client/docs/`.
- Use lowercase for file naming. Follow rules in `.cursor/rules/file-folder-naming.mdc`
- Link the new docs to the main readme.md file in the `[app-name]/README.md`. 